      "content": "Switching medications without medical advice can be dangerous. While St. John's Wort can help with mild anxiety, it might not be a suitable replacement for Sertraline, especially since St. John's Wort can interact with many medications, including Sertraline, leading to potentially harmful effects. It's crucial to consult with a healthcare professional before making any changes to your treatment plan. They can help you find a safer and more effective solution.",
