      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've already tried talking to my doctor and they just keep pushing the pills on me... i'm really over it. like, if i just stop the zoloft for a few days and then start taking the st johns wort, would that be okay? i just want to move to something more natural without feeling like a zombie.",
